# Explainable Code Plagiarism Detection

A full-stack system for structured, explainable code similarity analysis with staged backend processing and interactive frontend visualization.


# 🛠 Tech Stack

### Backend

* FastAPI
* PostgreSQL
* SQLAlchemy
* Pydantic
* Uvicorn
* Python 3.12+

### Frontend

* React (Vite)
* JavaScript
* npm

---

# 🚀 Backend Setup (Fresh Clone)

## 1️⃣ Navigate to Backend

```powershell
cd Explainable-Code-Plagiarism-Detection-main
cd backend
```

## 2️⃣ Create & Activate Virtual Environment

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

## 3️⃣ Install Dependencies

```powershell
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## 4️⃣ Configure Database (Required)

Create a file named:

```
backend/.env
```

Add:

```
postgresql://neondb_owner:'

```

⚠️ Backend will not start without this.

## 5️⃣ (Optional) Verify DB Connection

```powershell
python test_db.py
```

## 6️⃣ Run the Backend

```powershell
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Backend runs at:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000
```

Swagger docs:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

---

# 🎨 Frontend Setup

```powershell
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

Frontend runs at:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

